<section xml:id="ch1-section-looking-ahead" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Looking ahead</title>

    <p>
        In Chapter 2, we will dig deeper into the composition and structure of Earth's atmosphere,
        using a conceptual model of the atmosphere to assist us.
        This will give us necessary background for exploring through the rest of the textbook how Earth's atmosphere produces weather and climate.
    </p>

